{
  "stem": "27443.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I used to walk the street, which I was risking it, but I went-- I was able, this way, to go into a store and to get something to eat for the family.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I witnessed a lot of scenes like that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In 1939 when the war broke out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "As soon they-- and as soon they marched in into our town, my-- my city unfortunately became their-- not Lodz.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It became Litzmannstadt.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Litzmannstadt became one of their city.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It belonged to them, like a German city.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they occupied it, and they treated it-- anybody, any Jew was their trespasser, and they treated us likewise with all the cruel methods.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You see, we had no way of leaving.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "A lot of people that they were well off, through certain channels, they were able to leave.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Unfortunately, we were six people in our house, and my father was always working.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Considering we weren't poor, but we weren't rich either.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Well, our house never lacked of anything.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We had everything in our house.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We had everything.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But when it came out the war when my father stopped working, we were without funds, and I guess we were unable to leave at the time.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And nobody visualized that it's going to be that bad that we have to leave.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It formed a Judenrate.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It formed a Judenrate, which they also were talking that-- that in due time, they're going to make a ghetto.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they also advised, the Judenrate advised, that whoever has the means of leaving-- that means if you have enough money-- that you could maybe salvage your life.",
      "word_count": 28
    }
  ],
